    "body": "If you haven’t already, check out our [contributing guidelines](https://github.com/Expensify/ReactNativeChat/blob/main/contributingGuides/CONTRIBUTING.md) for onboarding and email contributors@expensify.com to request to join our Slack channel!\n___\n\n**Version Number:** v9.3.58-0\n**Reproducible in staging?:** Yes\n**Reproducible in production?:** Yes\n**If this was caught during regression testing, add the test name, ID and link from BrowserStack:** https://github.com/Expensify/App/pull/84769\n**Email or phone of affected tester (no customers):** htad26+eryeiuty@gmail.com\n**Issue reported by:** Applause Internal Team\n**Bug source:** Pull Request QA execution\n**Device used:** Windows 10 / Chrome, iOS 26.3 / iPhone 13, Android 11\n**App Component:** Money Requests\n\n## Action Performed:\n1. Create two workspaces\n2. Enable Taxes feature in one of them\n3. Create 2 scan expenses in those workspaces, one with tax (A), one without tax (B) accordingly\n4. Open A > More > Merge > Select B\n5. Select the report of B > Continue\n\n## Expected Result:\nThe confirmation step shows tax of A\n\n## Actual Result:\nThe confirmation step doesn't show tax amount of A. It is displayed as 0\n\n## Workaround:\nUnknown\n\n## Platforms:\n- [x] Android: App\n- [ ] Android: mWeb Chrome\n- [x] iOS: App\n- [ ] iOS: mWeb Safari\n- [ ] iOS: mWeb Chrome\n- [x] Windows: Chrome\n- [ ] MacOS: Chrome / Safari\n\n## Screenshots/Videos\n\nhttps://github.com/user-attachments/assets/2cac514e-e5c7-4670-a668-80835efb7485\n\n[View all open jobs on GitHub](https://github.com/Expensify/App/issues?q=is%3Aopen+is%3Aissue+label%3A%22Help+Wanted%22)\n\n<details><summary>Issue Owner</summary>Current Issue Owner: @Krishna2323</details>\n<details><summary>Upwork Automation - Do Not Edit</summary>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Upwork Job URL: https://www.upwork.com/jobs/~022042541732841216677</li>\n        <li>Upwork Job ID: 2042541732841216677</li>\n        <li>Last Price Increase: 2026-04-10</li>\n  