    "body": "If you haven’t already, check out our [contributing guidelines](https://github.com/Expensify/ReactNativeChat/blob/main/contributingGuides/CONTRIBUTING.md) for onboarding and email contributors@expensify.com to request to join our Slack channel!\n___\n\n**Version Number:** 9.3.55-0\n**Reproducible in staging?:** Y\n**Reproducible in production?:** Y (Redirects to staging after clicking book travel)\n**If this was caught during regression testing, add the test name, ID and link from BrowserStack:**\n**Email or phone of affected tester (no customers):**\n**Logs:** https://stackoverflow.com/c/expensify/questions/4856\n**Expensify/Expensify Issue URL:**\n**Issue reported by:** Applause Internal Team\n**Slack conversation** (hyperlinked to channel name): [More context here](https://github.com/Expensify/Expensify/issues/622044#issuecomment-4216397893)\n\n## Action Performed:\n\nPrecondition: Log in with an account that has Travel Beta enabled and enable Travel in the workspace.\n\nSteps to Reproduce:\n\n1. In NewDot, go to Workspaces → Members\n2. Invite a new user to the workspace\n3. Go to Global Create → Book Travel\n4. In the travel web page Navigate to Program → Users within Travel\n5. Verify that the newly invited user is created in Expensify Travel\n6. Go back to Workspaces → Members\n7. Select the added user\n8. Click “Remove from workspace”\n9. Return to Global Create → Book Travel\n10. In the travel web page Navigate to Program → Users within Travel\n## Expected Result:\nThe user removed from the workspace should also be removed from Expensify Travel.\n## Actual Result:\nThe user is not removed from Expensify Travel after being removed from the workspace.\n## Workaround:\nUnknown\n## Platforms:\nSelect the officially supported platforms where the issue was reproduced:\n- [ ] Android: App\n- [ ] Android: mWeb Chrome\n- [ ] iOS: App\n- [ ] iOS: mWeb Safari\n- [ ] iOS: mWeb Chrome\n- [x] Windows: Chrome\n- [x] MacOS: Chrome / Safari\n\n## Screenshots/Videos\n\nhttps://github.com/user-attachments/assets/bba061f9-70ab-4b4b-a4d2-b016861e3624\n\n[View all open jobs on GitHub](https://github.com/Expensify/App/issues?q=is%3Aopen+is%3Aissue+label%3A%22Help+Wanted%22)\n\n\n<details><summary>Issue Owner</summary>Current Issue Owner: @jjcoffee</details>\n<details><summary>Upwork Automation - Do Not Edit</summary>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Upwork Job URL: https://www.upwork.com/jobs/~022042345803404286496</li>\n        <li>Upwork Job ID: 2042345803404286496</li>\n        <li>Last Price Increase: 2026-04-09</li>\n    </ul>\n</details>",
